abstract: >-
  XPathGenie is an LLM-driven XPath auto-generation system that achieves
  87.3% hit rate and 95.0% semantic accuracy across 23 real-world websites
  through a novel pipeline of HTML compression, LLM inference, multi-page
  validation, and two-stage refinement.
